  "instructions": [
    "Heat butter in a large skillet over medium heat. ",
    "Add diced onion and saut\t4 until translucent, about 3-4 minutes. ",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes. ",
    "Add chopped plum tomatoes, salt, and pepper. Cook for 4-5 minutes, stirring occasionally. ",
    "Add khao khua and stir to combine. Cook for an additional 2-3 minutes. ",
    "Stir in lemon juice, lemon zest, and red pepper flakes. ",
    "Cook for an additional 1-2 minutes, stirring frequently. ",
    "Stir in chopped parsley and basil. ",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed."
